      "story": {
        "zh": "磨粉后干香就有很强烈的甜香，冲煮后入口即有强烈甜感。\n\n在口腔中呈现奶油般饱满丝滑的质地，温度下降后泛出莓果的微酸，尾韵持久，整体十分愉悦。",
        "en": "Even the dry grounds smell intensely sweet, and that sweetness lands the instant it touches your lips.\n\nThe body is full and silky — almost creamy. As it cools a gentle berry tartness emerges and the finish lingers. A thoroughly delightful cup."
      },
